Description: A novel approach to depict physical cell-cell interactions from scRNAseq datasets using cell type-specifc gene signatures.
             This method utilizes univariate linear models to identify and predict the cellular composition of multiplets in scRNAseq by assigning signature scores to cellular barcodes. 
